        <title>Extractive Industries Transparency Disclosure Act</title>
      </item>
      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To require, for the benefit of shareholders, the disclosure of payments to foreign governments for the extraction of natural resources, to allow such shareholders more appropriately to determine associated risks.</title>
